Ford Motor Co increased U.S. production schedule second quarter 52,000 car 32,000 truck previous plan , trade paper Ward's Automotive Reports said .
The paper , track industry production , said Ford plan build 485,000 car April-June period , compared 497,000 year ago .
Ford 's new production schedule represents 12 pct increase previous production plan car 10 pct truck , Ward 's said .
